[{"location":"index.html#CommonLH","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"This package collects general purpose code that does not \"fit\" into other packages with more well defined topics.","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#Checking-properties","page":"CommonLH","title":"Checking properties","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"check_float\ncheck_float_array","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.check_float","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.check_float","text":"check_float(x; lb, ub)\n\n\nCheck a scalar: should be real, finite, not nan, in optional bounds. Real is implied by being AbstractFloat.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.check_float_array","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.check_float_array","text":"check_float_array(m, lb, ub)\n\n\nCheck that a numeric array is finite, not NaN, and inside bounds.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#Array-operations","page":"CommonLH","title":"Array operations","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"bracket_array!\nscale_array!\nall_at_least\nall_at_most\nall_greater\nall_at_most\nany_greater\nany_less\nany_nan","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.scale_array!","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.scale_array!","text":"scale_array!(x, d, totalV)\n\n\nScale each \"row\" (along dimension d) of array x to match the totals given in totalV. The result satisfies\n\nsum(selectdim(x, d, j)) == totalV[j]\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#Vector-operations","page":"CommonLH","title":"Vector operations","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"bisecting_indices\nfind_indices\nfind_index","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.find_indices","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.find_indices","text":"find_indices(valueV, gridV; notFoundError)\n\n\nFor each value in valueV (a weakly increasing Vector), find the corresponding indices in gridV (also an increasing Vector{Integer}). If no match is found, set indices to 0. Returns a Vector even if only one value is given.\n\nExample\n\njulia> find_indices([2, 4], -2 : 2 : 10) == [3, 4]\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#Probabilities","page":"CommonLH","title":"Probabilities","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"The following operate on matrices that represent probabilities which sum to 1.","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"validate_prob_matrix\nvalidate_prob_vector\nprob_j\nprob_k\nprob_j_k\nprob_k_j\nev_given_j\nev_given_k\nscale_prob_array!","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.validate_prob_matrix","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.validate_prob_matrix","text":"validate_prob_matrix(probM)\n\n\nValidate a probability matrix. Elements are expected to sum to 1.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.validate_prob_vector","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.validate_prob_vector","text":"validate_prob_vector(probV)\n\n\nValidate a probability vector. Elements are expected to sum to 1.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.prob_j","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.prob_j","text":"Conditional probabilities of rows or columns given a probability matrix.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.prob_k","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.prob_k","text":"Conditional probabilities of rows or columns given a probability matrix.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.prob_j_k","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.prob_j_k","text":"prob_j_k(m, j, k)\n\n\nConditional probability (j | k).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.prob_k_j","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.prob_k_j","text":"prob_k_j(m, k, j)\n\n\nConditional probability (k | j).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.ev_given_j","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.ev_given_j","text":"ev_given_j(x, prM, j)\n\n\nCompute expected value of x, given row index j. Based on matrix of values xM[j,k] and matrix of probabilities (sum to 1) prM[j, k].\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.ev_given_k","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.ev_given_k","text":"ev_given_k(x, prM, k)\n\n\nCompute expected value of x, given column index k. Based on matrix of values xM[j,k] and matrix of probabilities (sum to 1) prM[j, k].\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.scale_prob_array!","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.scale_prob_array!","text":"scale_prob_array!(m; maxSum)\n\n\nGiven an array of probabilities: ensure that all are in [0, 1].  Error if bounds violation larger than rounding errors. Make sure that sum does not exceed an upper bound.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#Displaying-objects","page":"CommonLH","title":"Displaying objects","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"MultiIO\nshow_text_file\nshow_string_vector","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.MultiIO","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.MultiIO","text":"Object that holds multiple IO streams, so that a single print statement can be directed to all of them. Main use case: selectively write to optimization log and stdout. This must be a subtype of IO for dispatch to work correctly.\n\nBased on https://discourse.julialang.org/t/issues-with-println-buffering-output-when-redirecting-stdout-to-a-txt-file/23738/13\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.show_text_file","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.show_text_file","text":"show_text_file(filePath; io)\n\n\nShow a text file on the screen.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html#CommonLH.show_string_vector","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH.show_string_vector","text":"show_string_vector(sV)\nshow_string_vector(sV, width)\n\n\nDisplay string vector on fixed with screen.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"index.html","page":"CommonLH","title":"CommonLH","text":"","category":"page"}]
